      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like there’s nothing left inside. i used to see colors and shapes in everything, like the world was talking to me through the canvas. now it’s just... grey. silent. it's like the part of me that actually lived is just gone and there's nothing but this empty shell sitting in a room.",
