      "content": "but i don't think it's just a phase. it feels more permanent than that. like the engine has completely failed and there's just this heavy, useless metal casing left over. it’s exhausting to keep moving a body when the person who was driving it doesn't exist anymore. it just feels like i'm maintaining a museum for someone who died a long time ago.",
